{
  "title": "Sour Silky Jamaican Nectarine Curry",
  "description": "A light and refreshing Jamaican-inspired curry featuring nectarines, with a silky texture and a sour twist. This dish is perfect for warm weather and Mediterranean-friendly diets.",
